Source: cockpit-packagemanager
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Matti Airas <matti.airas@hatlabs.fi>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), nodejs, npm
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/hatlabs/cockpit-package-manager

Package: cockpit-packagemanager
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, cockpit (>= 276), packagekit
Description: Cockpit-based package manager using PackageKit
 A web-based package manager interface for Cockpit that provides:
  - Browse packages by Debian section
  - Search for packages by name or description
  - View detailed package information
  - Install and remove packages
  - View package dependencies
 .
 This package provides a modern, user-friendly interface for managing
 system packages through Cockpit's web interface.
